data.description: Welcome to this stunning new construction at 3548 Purdue Ave, located in the heart of Mar Vista! Upon entry, you're welcomed into an open-concept living space with high ceilings and beautiful natural light. The spacious living room includes a cozy fireplace and seamlessly flows with the dining area and gourmet kitchen, which features top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, and marble countertops with a large island. Upstairs, the primary suite is a true retreat with a private patio, luxurious en-suite bathroom, and a spacious walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms are also generously sized, each with its own full bathroom and ample closet space. One of the highlights of this home is the roof deck, with expansive outdoor space perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying the stunning views of the neighborhood and beyond. The ADU is spacious and stylish, complete with a full kitchen, washer dryer, full bathroom, and ample closet space. This flexible living space can easily be transformed into an office or a full living situation with a bed, depending on your needs. The ADU also has its own private entrance, making it perfect for guests, extended family, or as a rental unit. Located within the highly desirable Mar Vista Elementary School district, this home is perfect for families. The property also includes a 2-car garage and a driveway for additional parking. Don't miss this opportunity to own a stunning new construction in Mar Vista!
